{"tid":1718784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！集思廣益！被捕支援社工有野講！","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:20:02.000Z","uid":198864,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bca76816b8a40f78c2dec852784baa3743c7df5","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"我係社工，愈來愈多被捕手足要提堂，或者還押手足嘅家長要去探訪入野比佢。<br />\n<br />\n和你塞🙌🏻做到全城被罷工✅，但癱瘓交通亦令到手足有可能未能準時去到法院，家人去唔到收押所入野或者探訪，其實手足一定會諒解明白，但我地都要睇下可以點支援！<br />\n<br />\n我並唔係要叫停和你塞，但我地可以做啲咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n目前諗到係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">成立車隊</span></span>！<br />\n最好仲係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">電單車隊</span></strong></span>！<br />\n護送有需要嘅被捕手足同家屬去法院及收押所！<br />\nCU運送物資咁睇，電單車係不得了！<br />\n但係要考慮安全問題，未必個個敢坐電單車，<br />\n大家仲有冇諗到其他方法，<br />\n例如前一日比被捕手足去法院附近借宿？<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cccff8ed8cc49b11eb68bfb4ed897f72666aa4","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"集思廣益！"},{"pid":"2b86c2ac6a1b29f2b385f23fded522f9c2aff5a0","tid":1718784,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登嘅冷氣軍師，想幫手又冇得發夢嘅，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該幫手上Twitter，Reddit幫手！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線搏晒老命同班警甴對抗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你哋唔係連撳幾個掣都懶呀嘛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n美國議員繼續為香港發聲，大家快啲去回應支持啦～<br />\n<br />\n！！！提出法案嘅Marco Rubio話有好消息！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=320d24d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&h=c1718001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187</a><br />\n<br />\n！！！Dick Durbin促請Leader McConnell 就法案進行投票！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=e5c4e9c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953&h=47d24cbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Marsha Blackburn 繼續撐香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=0740592e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&h=56d542bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick Scott鬧黨媒冷血<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1194622539017752576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1194622539017752576&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=f60b011a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1194622539017752576&h=2e6ec6ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1194622539017752576</a><br />\n<br />\n！！眾議院Jim McGovern話唔好各打五十大板<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1194627617913069570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1194627617913069570&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=b4b79159\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1194627617913069570&h=c640462d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1194627617913069570</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">更加多嘅任務可以去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot，入\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A5&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=11e5d29d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot，入</a> /task 做任務。<br />\nadmin團隊會持續更新任務列表。</span></span>"},{"pid":"687c0121e79b02dfa72c642764d675e94060a31d","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"3e85ac4dd6bce07a07115e32727dc33087e36559","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7daabcd14a8f8c59655d460e267ce4c1fff45ab7","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"有冇有心人"},{"pid":"6d7599b0407a4cb64e273097d2fada03503bcc60","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"9672806ef5f15ea514265157e9e19101d2994559","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"可唔可以比啲意見"},{"pid":"9df51bd8fc02c6319bdaecb98f27c2f198a33f43","tid":1718784,"uid":198864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"569bc9d1a2874a3e2aaa21a6bb7982c376d5c008","t